  <div class="absolute top-0 transform -translate-x-1/2 -z-10 left-1/2">
    <%= render partial: "partials/home/few_more_things/bg" %>
  </div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0" style="box-shadow: inset 0 0 100px 100px #16161a"></div>
  <div class="relative text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold font-display md:text-4xl">
      <span class="gradient-heading">A</span>
      <span class="gradient-heading">few</span>
      <span class="gradient-heading">more</span>
      <span class="gradient-heading">things</span>
      <br class="hidden sm:inline" />
      <span class="gradient-heading">you</span>
      <span class="gradient-heading">may</span>
      <span class="gradient-heading">want</span>
      <span class="gradient-heading">to</span>
      <span class="gradient-heading">know</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-1 text-lg sm:max-w-xl text-gray-50">
      Security, community and transparency are things we value. Instead of just mentioning them, here’s how we’re
